data.description: Located in the heart of Port St John, this home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2-Bathrooms, and a 2-Car Garage.  Functionality in everyday living.  Loft ceilings over an Open living, Dining, and Kitchen area increase the open spaciousness feeling. The spacious Master Bedroom features a walk-in closet and both guest bedrooms still have plenty of space for King Size beds.  Enjoy the extra convenience of an expanded screened in back Porch, for additional entertainment or relaxation space, overlooking the large fenced yard.  New to Florida, or looking for a little extra sense of security during our summer storms? Rest easy with Hurricane Impact Windows and a new Roof, both installed in 2022. Seller offering $2,000 closing cost credit for qualifying offer.
